"gives translations by Manfred Krebernik (published at the Rencontre Assyriologique International, Innsbruck, 2018) and\n"
"identifies the Akkadian words with celestial regions and constellations (work by Susanne M. Hoffmann, 2015-2018, presented at Deutsche Orientalisten-Tagung, Jena, 2017).</p>\n"
