"<sup>ESTRELLA</sup><i>LA&#7722;RU</i>(Oveja)</td>\n"
"<td></td>\n"
"<td>&alpha; UMa (+)</td>\n"
"</tr>\n"
"<tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #e7e6e6\">\n"
"<td>17</td>\n"
"<td><sup>ESTRELLA</sup>MU.BU.K&Eacute;&Scaron;.DA (¿Yugo enganchado?)</td>\n"
"<td></td>\n"
"<td>UMi</td>\n"
"</tr>\n"
"<tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #e7e6e6\">\n"
"<td>18</td>\n"
"<td><sup>ESTRELLA</sup>MAR.G&Iacute;D.DA.AN.NA (Vagón del cielo)</td>\n"
"<td></td>\n"
"<td>¿algún lugar entre UMi y Vega?</td>\n"
"</tr>\n"
"<tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #e7e6e6\">\n"
"<td>19</td>\n"
"<td>ESTRELLA en su enlace: <sup>ESTRELLA</sup><i>APIL-EMA&#7722;</i> (Heredero\n"
"del templo Ema&#7723;-)</td>\n"
"<td></td>\n"
"<td>&alpha; UMi (?)</td>\n"
