" - [#6]: Cenev, Gjore (2008). _ Constelaciones populares macedonias. Publicaciones del Observatorio Astronómico de Belgrado, vol. 85, p. 97-109. Belgrado, Serbia. [Enlace](http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2008POBeo..85...97C)\n"
" - [#7]: Cenev, Gjore (2014). _The Ancient Sky Map of the Macedonian People._ Cosmos - The Journal of the Traditional Cosmology Society, volumen 30, Edimburgo, Escocia, Reino Unido. [Enlace](http://www.academia.edu/18707131/The_Ancient_Sky_Map_Of_The_Macedonian_People)"

